                            <Label
							VerticalOptions="Center"
							Text="WJPUKI"
							FontSize="30"
                            TextColor="#09052e"
							FontFamily="Times Roman"/>


                            <Grid>
                                <!-- Category -->
                                <Label
								Text="ABOUT US"
								TextColor="#ff5e14"
								FontSize="16"
								VerticalOptions="Center" />

                            </Grid>

                            <!-- Text block 1 -->
                            <Grid Margin="0,5,0,10">
                                <Label
                                   TextColor="#09052e"
							Text="Wjpuki is one of the leading Anime shops in the country, specializing in selling and accepting orders for figure models, toys, keychains, toys, costumes and cosplay accessories of all kinds. If you are a fan of Manga-Anime, you can't help but come to the shop, you can find yourself manga characters that since childhood have been attached to you through comic books like Doraemon cat, or Doraemon. Detective from the famous Conan to the naughty robot Arale with 2 Boco kids and also can't ignore the famous characters in OnePiece, Dragon Ball and many other characters in the story like Gintama, Naruto, or Anime are playing. very hot are Jujutsu Kaisen, Hololive, Date A Live..v… etc.
And if you are a big fan of animated movies like Pixar, Disney: ToyStory, Incredible, etc. or blockbuster Hollywood movies like Batman, Avenger, Ironman, Hulk, .. then you can't ignore it." />

                            </Grid>

                            <Grid>
                                <!-- Category -->
                                <Label
								Text="OUR MISSION"
								TextColor="#ff5e14"
								FontSize="16"
								VerticalOptions="Center" />

                            </Grid>


                            <!-- Text block 2 -->
                            <Grid Margin="0,5,0,10">
                                <Label
                                     TextColor="#09052e"
							Text="Each product of Wjpuki is carefully crafted with the hands of skilled craftsmen, selected by the shop to be imported very carefully. Carefully selected materials and hundreds of spoiled colors combine with modern thinking and sophisticated design to deliver high quality products to consumers. Each decorative accessory bearing the stamp of TEE Beauty Tool shop has won thousands of hearts of customers in Ho Chi Minh City in particular and all over the country in general.

