Not only bringing a very high fashion look, but Wjpuki's genuine items are also a lovely gift for boys to give their girlfriends on the occasion of their birthday or love anniversary..!" />
                            </Grid>



                            <Grid
							Margin="-20,0">
                                <!--Gallery-->
                                <Image
								Source="logo.jfif"
								HeightRequest="160"
								>
                                </Image>
                            </Grid>

                            <Grid>
                                <!-- Category -->
                                <Label
								Text="OUR UNIQUE SERVICE OFFERING"
								TextColor="#ff5e14"
								FontSize="16"
								VerticalOptions="Center" />

                            </Grid>

                            <Grid Margin="0,5,0,10">
                                <Label
                                    TextColor="#09052e"
							Text="Receive free shipping within HO CHI MINH city (1km radius) (applicable to orders over 300,000).

For orders on the website, the shop will call to confirm the order and report the shipping fee to the customer, the goods will be sent after the customer agrees with the shipping fee.

Ship COD goods nationwide, express delivery with reasonable fees. " />
                            </Grid>

                            <Grid>
                                <Label
								Text="CONTACT US"
								TextColor="#ff5e14"
								FontSize="16"
								VerticalOptions="Center" />

                            </Grid>

                            <Grid Margin="0,5,0,10">
                                <Label
                                    TextColor="#09052e"
							Text="For further support you can call our helpline,visit us or email us using the options below" />
                            </Grid>
                            <Grid>
                                <Label
								Text="OUR ADDRESS"
								TextColor="#ff5e14"
								FontSize="16"
								VerticalOptions="Center" />

                            </Grid>

                            <Grid Margin="0,5,0,10">
                                <Label
                                    TextColor="#09052e"
							Text="KTX Khu B ĐHQG TPHCM." />
                            </Grid>

                            <Grid>
                                <Label
								Text="OUR EMAIL ADDRESS"
								TextColor="#ff5e14"
								FontSize="16"
								VerticalOptions="Center" />

                            </Grid>

                            <Grid Margin="0,5,0,10">
                                <Label
                                    TextColor="#09052e"
							Text="info@wjpuki.com.vn" />
                            </Grid>
                            <Frame HasShadow="True"
                           Padding="5"
                           Margin="0,10,0,10"
                           CornerRadius="30">
                                <Entry Text=""  Placeholder="Type info@swiftgas.co.za here!!!" x:Name="EntryEmail"/>
                            </Frame>

                            <Frame HasShadow="True"
                           Padding="5"
                           Margin="0,10,0,10"
                           CornerRadius="30">
                                <Entry  Text="" Placeholder="Subject" x:Name="EntrySubject"/>
                            </Frame>
                            <Button Text="Submit"
                    Margin="10"
                    BackgroundColor="#ff5e14"
                    TextColor="White"
                    FontSize="Medium"
                    CornerRadius="30" 
                    Clicked="Button_Clicked"/>

                        </StackLayout>
                    </Frame>

                </Grid>


            </StackLayout>

        </ScrollView>
    </ContentPage.Content>
</ContentPage>